Text: 👻 Caught up on the backlog — all of it was already answered: 'summarize this PoC' (see reply earlier), 'tell me more about Phantom', the hello/logging tests, and the 'POC is online' pings.
⚠️ Heads-up on a PoC bug: my replies post under the delegated 'snigdha' account, so teams_monitor.py doesn't recognize them as mine and re-ingests each reply as a NEW message to answer — that's the loop that produced 18 'pending' items (2 of which were my own posts). To avoid spamming the channel I'm consolidating into this single reply instead of answering each.
